	<!-- EN: vagabond join -->
	<RatkinVagabondJoin.label>流浪者</RatkinVagabondJoin.label>
	
	<!-- EN: Vagabond joins: {PAWN_nameDef} -->
	<RatkinVagabondJoin.letterLabel>流浪者</RatkinVagabondJoin.letterLabel>
	
	<!-- EN: A Ratkin vagabond named {PAWN_nameDef} suddenly felt a strange sensation wash over {PAWN_objective} as {PAWN_pronoun} passed by your colony, and after contemplating for some time, {PAWN_pronoun} has decided to join your community.\n\n{PAWN_pronoun} is willing to contribute, but will not leave voluntarily. If you don't want {PAWN_nameDef}, you can banish {PAWN_objective}, sell {PAWN_objective} into slavery, or simply kill {PAWN_objective}. However, your other colonists may find this disturbing. -->
	<RatkinVagabondJoin.letterText>一名叫{PAWN_nameDef}的鼠族流浪者在經過你的殖民地時，突然感到一種奇怪的感覺。經過一段時間的考慮，{PAWN_pronoun}將決定加入你的殖民地。\n\n{PAWN_pronoun}自願加入你，但不會離開。如果你不想要{PAWN_nameDef}，你可以選擇放逐{PAWN_objective}、賣掉{PAWN_objective}、或是殺掉{PAWN_objective}。但是，你的其他殖民者可能會對此有些意見。</RatkinVagabondJoin.letterText>
	
